    "com/ zyb19 84/ Pharm acolo gy-LLM-test-set) platforms for easy access by other users.",
    "Additionally, based on this test set, the baseline 'question-answer' scenarios and scoring outcomes for GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 can be found in the document's appendix.",
    "Evaluation of Pharmacologica Test Set Based on General LLMs The Accessibility of ChatGPT in Pharmacologica Test SetEssential attribute evaluations, such as contextual consistency, semantic similarity, and consistency tests, are fundamental for assessing the capabilities of general LLMs like GPT-3.5, GPT-4, Llama2, Claude, PaLM, and specialized LLMs like DrugChat, DrugGPT, and Mol-Instructions in handling question-answering tasks [45]."
